##### ENVIRONMENT 
```
```

##### CONFIGURATION
```
process morebacon {
	encoder json;
	run /usr/bin/morebacon;
}

neighbor 10.1.1.2 {
    description "10.1.1.2";
    router-id 10.1.1.1;
