    }
    api {
	    processes [morebacon];
	    neighbor-changes;
	    receive {
	        parsed;
	        update;
	    }
    }
}
```


##### SUMMARY
tcp.once exits without reaping child processes. 

##### STEPS TO REPRODUCE
Start exa from long running daemon process with tcp.once flag.

##### EXPECTED RESULTS
Expect exa to shutdown gracefully on bgp session termination.

##### ACTUAL RESULTS
Exa exits without reaping child processes, leaving behind zombies. 

##### IMPORTANCE
Accumulation of zombies over time is causing devops to panic.

